javax.sip.header
Interface MediaType

All Known Subinterfaces:
AcceptHeader, ContentTypeHeader
public interface MediaType

This interface represents media type methods for any header that contain content type and content sub-type values.

Author:
BEA Systems, NIST
See Also:
AcceptHeader, ContentTypeHeader
